Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:40.47,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I found out…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.60,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn’t strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.20,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nor was I weak…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:51.23,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,There was no hatred…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.00,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,No anger…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:56.98,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Only…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.00,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai…eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.53,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that’s not your way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:13.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of saying your Spirit Energy \Nhas fully returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:14.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.74,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Want to find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.23,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You guys wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.58,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll finish this in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:32.79,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t push your luck with \Nsome makeshift Bankai….
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.36,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:00.86,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:09.64,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.61,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Kon! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.30,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you saying, Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.21,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t stand here and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.72,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Kon…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:19.59,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this, we should \Nbe fighting together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:22.11,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,How much rest do you guys need?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.55,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve rested enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.92,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t know when \Nto shut up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:31.88,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.42,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.51,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.76,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on going…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.27,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.25,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Somenomai, Tsukishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.08,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You people never learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.15,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.88,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one causing trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.94,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,El Directo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:21.43,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.37,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 73: Soren Sokatsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:39.17,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.47,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Getsuga…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.03,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Tensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.32,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,He’s unable to absorb \NKurosaki’s Getsuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:10.01,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,As we suspected, Kageroza is \Nunable to harness Hollow powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.42,B2,KAGEROZA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s more powerful… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:23.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Wondering why my Getsugatensho \Nis more powerful now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of losing my Spirit Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.37,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally realized \Nit once I lost my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.10,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Realized what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.94,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That I can’t stand the thought
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of regretting without \Ngiving my best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.56,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I will defeat you with \Neverything I’ve got!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:43.49,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I admit that you are different \Ncompared to when we last fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:44.82,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.16,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,It hardly matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.43,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Is he manipulating space again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:55.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:59.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,capturing Kageroza will be difficult, \Nmuch less saving Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.81,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some way to save Kujo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.63,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Chain and Soul Sleep…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:08.57,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,The two vital points of a soul, if \Nwe can shatter his Soul Chain…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.16,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I get it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.16,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,If we stop the flow of Spirit \NEnergy within his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s a chance that he \Nwill split back into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:16.77,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.55,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Chain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:19.23,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Kon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.11,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.57,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go tell Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.45,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the best you \Ncan do with the help
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of your so-called friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.37,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Or has your Spirit Energy \Ncompletely run out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.47,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.57,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can save Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.13,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,and protect my friends, \Nthen it doesn’t matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.84,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\NI’ll end it quickly for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:52.39,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The strap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.12,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I was waiting for…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:17.20,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.33,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.42,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:22.58,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.34,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.26,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.97,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.31,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Getsuga…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Tensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.35,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Did we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:35.75,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you… Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.14,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,happening to my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:53.78,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,My head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:59.04,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.23,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.43,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.95,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Finish us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.03,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,This is our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:21.74,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.52,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:27.92,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.65,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Shatter his Soul Chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.77,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.57,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting a futile battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.77,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You think…I’ve lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:11.46,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll show you if it’s futile or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:18.04,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,If I’m going to lose this body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.90,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.09,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Renzan: Hajokuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:32.86,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:02.74,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.01,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.38,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.49,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What is this Spiritual Pressure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.26,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.28,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,He still had this much power left?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:23.07,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,No, this Spiritual Pressure is the \NReishi of the Soul Society itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:26.00,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,He’s absorbing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:28.89,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.61,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to deal with \Nthat kind of Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:35.54,B2,HISAGI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,This wasn’t part of the plan…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.10,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:55.18,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear you guys weren’t \Nexpecting this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:59.69,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.80,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,So much force with \Njust a single blast…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.92,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:08.99,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s growing bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.36,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,I think we’re in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.53,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. We have to act fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.17,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:19.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Danku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.78,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Yama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:33.16,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Kageroza Inaba’s, or should I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:38.01,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Ouko Yushima’s every scheme is spurred
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by vengeance against the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:48.03,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,He intends to destroy the \NSoul Society along with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.67,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:13:00.69,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Never did I dream the \Nend would be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:03.34,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,But, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:06.39,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Ichigo Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.56,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,to that place between \Nchaos and nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.02,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s getting bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.45,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s up to us to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:18.99,B2,KOMAMURA (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.53,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Reigai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.39,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,You people…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.66,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Going for an all-out attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.94,B2,HITSUGAYA (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,That’s not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:39.31,B2,UKITAKE (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Do you recall, Master Genryusai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.97,B2,UKITAKE (REIGAI) (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Certainly, to the real ones,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:47.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what we’re doing might seem like \Na simple rebellion by imposters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.27,B2,UKITAKE (REIGAI) (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But we Reigai have our way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of following through \Nwith what we believe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.51,B2,GENRYUSAI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And what is that? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.35,B2,UKITAKE (REIGAI) (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We cannot tell you just yet. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.22,B2,UKITAKE (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,The time has come for you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to understand the \Nmeaning of those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:03.73,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:07.39,B2,HITSUGAYA (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,You claim that what you protect \Nis very clear to you—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and it is for us, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:13.70,B2,HITSUGAYA (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,We will protect the Soul \NSociety in our own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.75,B2,UKITAKE (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,It is the duty of us Mod Souls to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a fellow Mod Soul who \Nhas gone out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.05,B2,UKITAKE (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:22.71,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.14,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,They’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.45,B2,SHUNSUI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Oh well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:56.85,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:58.73,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not stopping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:03.63,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:10.69,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve done enough…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:14.57,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.56,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.90,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi! What’re you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.17,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:58.55,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they had pride, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.31,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:06.46,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just barely…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.48,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ichigo… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.63,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your invasion force
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:25.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,didn’t work out the way you planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.67,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Now all that’s left \Nis to rescue Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.13,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.13,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Why can’t I defeat you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.59,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.79,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Why can’t I defeat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.66,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,What drives you this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:02.79,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:08.63,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:13.21,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You have something to protect, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.84,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You have friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.23,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,To be there for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:19.23,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,To shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.61,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,To be close to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:29.43,B2,KAGEROZA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only the weak would seek \Nthe aid of others… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:31.07,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,So why…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:35.90,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.23,B2,NOZOMI (N),0000,0000,0000,,We found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:56.47,B2,NOZOMI (N),0000,0000,0000,,We weren’t strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:58.44,B2,NOZOMI (N),0000,0000,0000,,nor were we weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.15,B2,NOZOMI (N),0000,0000,0000,,There was no hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:02.89,B2,NOZOMI (N),0000,0000,0000,,No anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:08.20,B2,NOZOMI (N),0000,0000,0000,,Only that we were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:19.81,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:25.19,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Were we…mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:29.19,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.38,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.12,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.15,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:58.67,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kon…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.16,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I’m all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.05,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Your right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.46,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:11.15,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all’s good now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.54,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:16.33,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,C’mon, let’s go back to the \NWorld of the Living, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:21.77,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:23.61,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.44,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.48,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,This was the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.57,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, what’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:46.93,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kon…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.93,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,This is as it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.08,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you talking about, Nozomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.92,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing good about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.98,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,At the very end, I told him…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:59.13,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I would be his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:00.45,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.89,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I learned what it meant \Nto have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:07.43,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Now it’s my turn to teach him…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.23,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:12.06,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,It’s like you’re going \Nto disappear forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.66,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let you do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.35,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for this, Kon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:23.57,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I…couldn’t protect you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.34,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.85,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You did protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:30.31,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,We were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.03,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,But we’re at peace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:35.13,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s because all of you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.95,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Because Ichigo, and you were there, Kon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.73,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I’m there for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.68,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be there for you! So…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:49.44,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, I couldn’t \Nhear it…but now I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.39,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,The voice of my soul deep inside me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.02,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear it, Kon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.17,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t hear deep inside of you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:20:59.61,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:02.85,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,If you let me put my ear to your \Nbreast, I’d be willing to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.70,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a pervert, \Nyou know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:11.64,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Well pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.16,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t forget us…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:17.74,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.84,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we’ll always be…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:33.24,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Friends…forever…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there’s something I want to say
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:23.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,before we head back to \Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:24.62,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:25.74,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Let it all out while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:26.74,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:29.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai, Bankai, Bankai, \NBankai, Bankai, Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:31.18,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:32.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m stacking up on \Nmy call outs since I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,won’t be able to do them for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:38.76,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:40.14,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.60,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Let me return this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:44.36,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped it in the Precipice \NWorld, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:45.07,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.83,0:23:47.19,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:48.47,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:49.53,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:51.99,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,I have one for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:55.28,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:57.89,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I have something a lot better!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.11,0:24:01.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let’s all head back \Nto the World of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:03.31,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,-Right.\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:05.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,